    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 36 to define \"employee\"; and \"employer\" provide employment protections for members of the Civil Air Patrol in private businesses and local governments; amend KRS 61.394 to extend state government employment protections to members of the Civil Air Patrol."
    }
